name: Crusaders of the Surfed Dunes
description: Hailing from the Dunes of Kathoon, the Crusaders of the Surfed Dunes are known for their adept handling of dune surfers. Now almost finished uncovering the details about chronomancers and their magics from aeons past, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
